front.title: •Zuckuss In Mist Hunter
front.gametext: May add 1 pilot and 3 passengers. Permanent pilot is •Zuckuss, who provides ability of 4 and adds 2 to power. Unless opponent has total ability > 6 piloting here, may reset opponent's total battle destiny here to 0.
front.lore: Zuckuss is a dangerous adversary, especially when aboard his own starship. Mystical omens enable the Gand to predict enemy maneuvers in starship combat.

combo: Zuckuss In Mist Hunter + 4-LOM With Concussion Rifle Two battle destinies.
Zuckuss In Mist Hunter + 4-LOM With Concussion Rifle + Boba Fett, Bounty Hunter Four battle destinies.
